The Governor of Abia State, Okezie Ikpeazu, has approved the appointment of Dr. Ndubuisi Davidson Wokoh as the Chairman of the Governing Council of the Abia State University Teaching Hospital Aba. The new appointment was made known in a press release forwarded to DAILY POST, by Onyebuchi Ememanka, Chief Press Secretary to the State Governor, on Thursday evening. According to the release, “Dr. Wokoh is a Consultant Obstetrician and Gynecologist with the Federal Medical Center Umuahia. “This appointment which is with immediate effect supersedes any previous appointment in this regard.”